OL,3,CSNP minister suspended from Scottish
OL,4,CParliament over #11,000 iPad roaming
OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FLater announcing he would cover the
OL,8,Fcosts himself, Mr Matheson revealed
OL,9,Fthe bill had been the result of his
OL,10,Fchildren using the device as a WiFi
OL,11,Fhotspot to watch football during a
OL,12,Fholiday in Morocco.
OL,14,FThe former minister initially denied
OL,15,Fthere had been any inappropriate use
OL,16,Fof the device, when asked by
OL,17,Fjournalists.
OL,19,FAfter months of pressure on him, Mr
OL,20,FMatheson stood down as health
OL,21,Fsecretary in February.
