OL,5,Cbill
OL,7,FThe SNP MSP's punishment was handed
OL,8,Fdown by the Standards, Procedures and
OL,9,FPublic Appointments Committee at
OL,10,FHolyrood on Thursday. It will now be
OL,11,Fsubject to a vote in the Parliament.
OL,13,FIt will no doubt increase pressure on
OL,14,FMr Matheson to stand down as an MSP,
OL,15,Fgiven the Scottish Parliament has no
OL,16,Fway of removing elected members in the
OL,17,Fway the UK Parliament does.
