OL,7,FSouth of the border, a suspension of
OL,8,F10 sitting days is enough to spark a
OL,9,Frecall petition, which allows
OL,10,Fconstituents to remove an MP if 10%
OL,11,Fsign the document.
OL,13,FThis was most recently used in
OL,14,FRutherglen and Hamilton West following
OL,15,Fthe breach of Covid regulations by
OL,16,Fformer SNP MP Margaret Ferrier and
OL,17,Fresulted in Labour taking the seat
OL,18,Fwith a massive swing.
